Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:33.73,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}何故　どうして？広い世界の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:39.60,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}運命は　この場所に　私を導いたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:44.80,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}繋ぐ手と手　戸惑う私のため
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:51.05,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}受け取った優しさ　きっと忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:56.90,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}その場しのぎの笑顔で　傍観してるより
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.62,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}本当の気持ちで…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:59.69,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}その場しのぎの笑顔で　傍観してるより
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:07.09,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&} 本当の気持ちで　向かい合う自分でいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:11.91,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}きっと　どこまでも行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:14.87,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}見えない　未来へも飛べる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:20.05,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}この気持ちと　君の気持ち　重なればきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.93,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}We are one　一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:26.07,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}Hold your hand　心はいつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:28.86,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}今を生き抜く為に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:34.14,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}私たちは　出会ったのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:39.67,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}私ト云ウ 音響キ ソノ先ニ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:46.18,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,500)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}微笑みをSing out with us

Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:33.73,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}为何 为什么? 在这广阔的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:39.60,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}是命运把我引导到这地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:44.80,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}紧握的双手 为了困惑的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:51.05,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}一定不会忘记这从你得到的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:56.90,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}比起在场摆着敷衍的笑容旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.62,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}真正的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:59.69,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}比起在场摆着敷衍的笑容旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:07.09,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}更想直面自己真正的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:11.91,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}无论哪里都一定能去到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:14.87,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}飞向看不到的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:20.05,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}这份心情与你的心情能重合的话一定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.93,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}我们同心 一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:26.07,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}心里一直都与你双手紧扣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:28.86,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}我们现在为了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:34.14,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}也许就能够邂逅到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:39.67,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,100)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}响起名为我的音乐 从此以后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:46.18,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,500)}{\3c&H3CAAFA&}用这微笑 Sing out with us
